---
layout: layouts/base.njk
title: "Effective Hallucinations"
permalink: /AIblog/
bodyClass: aiblog
---

<div class="aiblog-header">
  <h1 class="aiblog-title">Effective <span>Hallucinations</span></h1>
  <p class="aiblog-tagline">Conversations with AI about nonprofits, philanthropy, and the social sector.</p>
</div>

<ul class="post-list">
  {% for post in collections.aiblog %}
  <li>
    <p class="post-meta">{{ post.date | readableDate }}</p>
    <h2><a href="{{ post.url }}">{{ post.data.title }}</a></h2>
    {% if post.data.description %}<p class="post-excerpt">{{ post.data.description }}</p>{% endif %}
  </li>
  {% endfor %}
</ul>
